Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}复仇女神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蒙古鲁雇佣的杀手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深感荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和曾率领赛姆打败蒙古鲁军的豹战士交手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 赢不了我们兄弟俩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自吹自擂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们最初就只是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的弟弟只不过是影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼亚伊路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的尼亚伊路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经嫉妒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你出生之后 我还想继续做父亲最疼爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才挥剑骑马 身着男装
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大公殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看来你和尼亚伊路长的真像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以往我没有发现 你和尼亚伊路像你们的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里就为了说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是你结婚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧 布拉多大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼亚伊路死后身子骨变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早点见到继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早点出嫁 生个男孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是物品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我是蒙古鲁唯一的公主 但我也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国目前正处于什么状况之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不正是听从父亲的命令去了帕罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才遭此下场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自尤诺的急报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下再说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕这是刻不容缓的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库里斯塔鲁宫殿已经落入反叛军之手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且领军的是库里斯塔鲁公爵 阿鲁多·纳利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多·纳利斯并没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼时被杀的是替身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行凶者阿斯托利亚斯也被帕罗的人操纵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外各地的叛乱都是阿鲁多·纳利斯的计谋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都可以说是计谋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召集所有人 召开军事会议
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到你这样的人 也被人彻底欺骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿慕涅莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:05:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴吗 你高兴吗 阿慕涅莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 这肯定是哪里搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位温柔的纳利斯大人会欺骗公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情根本无法想像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说一切都搞错了 那个人果然还是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我依靠着和他的回忆还能活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 弗洛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一会就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:06:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是实际上你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更本不可能会搞错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更本...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何而哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了失去的爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了受伤的心？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被自以为爱着自己的男人如此残酷地背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手无策 嚎啕大哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您振作 阿慕涅莉丝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我准备军队的正装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有给房间的壁炉点上火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人 您这是干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵 我要割去我内心中的女性部分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这也太...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没经历过恋爱的你不会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在对我来说最痛苦的并不是被那个男人背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被如此残酷地背叛 我还爱着那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心是多么悲惨、多么令人厌恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才必须舍弃身为女人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被他的双眼注视
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他呼唤着我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的内心不会再变得软弱无力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像你点燃的火焰 会烧尽你自己一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会离开你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩因恨而纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的头发怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢弃身为女人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为右府将军也作为蒙古鲁公主完成我的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我誓言的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好的决心 阿慕涅莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大公殿下 请务必派我去镇压帕罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我阿慕涅莉丝豁出性命也惩罚帕罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死阿鲁多·纳利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 任命右府将军阿慕涅莉丝镇压帕罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见过的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁古斯的弟兄们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻越威廉山脉的勇士们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们终于来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后顺着这条路一直走 很快就是帕罗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不去帕罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多·纳利斯已经夺回了库里斯塔鲁宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古鲁恐怕会派出帕罗镇压军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要痛击帕罗镇压军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我们要前往帕罗和蒙古鲁的国境
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是斯卡卢大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果蒙古鲁没有派出帕罗镇压军的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗 进攻蒙古鲁的心脏托拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次该轮到我们扫平蒙古鲁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是阿鲁古斯的黑恶魔斯卡卢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这情报貌似也能高价卖给帕罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等好了 阿鲁多·纳利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古鲁引以为豪的骑士团总数五万
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布拉多大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经什么都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上只有两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛了我的你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和要杀死你的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说阿慕涅莉丝率领五万兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从托拉斯出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是纳利斯大人已经妙策在胸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么计策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人还是对自己人也小心提防
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我在纳利斯大人就不会落入阿慕涅莉丝手中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望纳利斯大人能表露真心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只向我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是属于琳达大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您还这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.03,0:13:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将自断性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你爱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 但是你并不爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就像爱着忠诚的看门狗一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我这样就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳利斯大人请保持现在的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像伊莉丝一般美丽、冷酷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晨有个奇妙之人跨越了帕罗的国境
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇妙之人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占星盘显示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大的红色之星从胜利之宫而来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色之星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利之宫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎重起见 我派人去监视了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带他来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣骑士团万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢南大人万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达巴鲁斯大人、达路贡大人万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在各地发动起帕罗解放军的圣骑士团凯旋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就混在他们当中进入库里斯塔鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 旅人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您掉东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库里斯塔鲁公爵 阿鲁多·纳利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙就是阿鲁多·纳利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达的未婚夫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴拉基亚的伊修特邦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我 你来这的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看 这是在阿古纳亚得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面是这样写的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上沿海州海军为了封锁罗斯港而出动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后在罗斯暗杀阿古纳亚王博鲁格·巴联
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投靠蒙古鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这情报无误的话 就大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的守护神铎莱顿之名 这封密信是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你 帕罗不会因为背后袭击而倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有另一个情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在威廉山脉北麓的红色街道目睹了斯卡卢军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢说要去迎击来自蒙古鲁的帕罗镇压军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鞑念湿地消失的斯卡卢翻越了威廉山脉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个天然屏障？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡卢就是这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道世上还有不可能这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳利斯大人 我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请雇佣我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将在下作为您的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是作为一柄剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这代价还真是便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸上这样写着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我很贵哦”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,价格我自己定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要的只是一扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后建功立业 凭自己的本领出人头地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来你会给我带来幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想把你编入骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你就待在我身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修特邦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人不多 别怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久阿慕涅莉丝大人的援军就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古鲁是个年轻的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队的确强大 不过指挥体系统薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个兵团只要白骑士不下达命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑骑士就不会独自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么瞄准传令系统
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各队之间的传令系统已经被切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我摆猛牛之阵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛牛之阵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是蝎子的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用钢铁鳞片保护身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用尖刺蜇人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有打破那个阵势的计策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准腹部的话 其实是很脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴莱由斯会给我好好干的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌报 各部的佣兵不断向帕罗投降
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕罗的奸细潜入我军
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游说我军倒戈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有人能自由进入我军铁壁般的防线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这里就有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不知道帕罗有名的魔道士部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰兰到底也不是我们的对手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是阿鲁多·纳利斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭 敌袭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是草原之民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正是蒙古鲁公主、右府将军阿慕涅莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率领草原蛮族的是何人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上名 与我一战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别笑人了 蒙古鲁的调皮公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调皮公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是 奎因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意和你单挑 丢光男人面子的大将
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:21:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是斯卡卢 人称阿鲁古斯的黑恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁古斯的斯卡卢 你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我是斯卡卢还想和我单挑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就陪你过招
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下请您退后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弩箭队 射击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点能耐吗 阿慕涅莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.82,0:21:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇猛的蒙古鲁军 给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 暂时先撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报 白骑士总指挥官泰兰大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在兰兹贝鲁战死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古鲁三万军队也全面溃败
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃帕罗的贝克公爵·樊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿慕涅莉丝 把命留下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是那个人的计策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人连我的怨恨都不愿意正面接受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕 不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鲁多·纳利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变幻无常的命运所指引的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一颗看透一切的明星
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便所走的道路不同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.76,0:24:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心却总是在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这片星光闪烁的天空之下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 在怎样的明星之下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.96,0:24:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在亚安的指引下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:56.97,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}This is my road 導かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:05.11,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}Here I stand ここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:12.09,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}父と母の 遠い面影（記憶）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:20.27,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}瞳閉じれば 聞こえる声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:30.33,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}This is my road 歩いてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:38.68,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}果たしない時もう越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:44.69,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}This is my life 扉を開け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:55.68,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}定め（運命）と共に 今、道（伝説）を刻んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:56.97,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}这是我的道路 被指引着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:05.11,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}你依然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:12.09,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}父母渐渐消逝的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:20.27,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}闭上眼睛依然可闻的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:30.33,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}这是我的道路 大步向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:38.68,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}无尽岁月已经度过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:44.69,ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,250)}这是我的生活 大门向我敞开
